# Optional secrets. Copy to .env (gitignored) for local runs. None are required:
# the NBA pipeline uses ESPN and the NBL pipeline uses the public nbl.com.au API,
# both anonymous and cloud-reachable. The WNBA pipeline uses stats.wnba.com,
# which is anonymous but IP/geo-walled for cloud runners (run it locally/AU).

# Optional: a browser session cookie for stats.nba.com, used only by the
# best-effort NBA enrichment step. Leave unset to skip it (ESPN covers everything).
# NBA_COOKIE=

# Optional bookmaker-odds (odds.py) overrides for WNBA outright/futures markets.
# Defaults are sensible (WNBA futures sit under Sportsbet's US basketball class 16);
# set these only if a book splits WNBA out or exposes a specific outright event id.
# SB_WNBA_FUTURES_CLASS=16
# LAD_WNBA_FUTURES_EVENT=
